  "title": "Social Media Marketing Intern",
  "description": "<p>What We Are Looking For<br>\n<br>\n<br>\nSocial Media Internship (Part time &amp; Full time)<br>\n3 month/ 6 months<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<img alt=\"✅\" src=\"https://web.telegram.org/a/img-apple-64/2705.png\"/> Generating Viral Ideas – Brainstorm, research, and execute trending content strategies.<br>\n<img alt=\"✅\" src=\"https://web.telegram.org/a/img-apple-64/2705.png\"/> Editing Videos (CapCut &amp; Other Tools) – Create engaging short-form videos for TikTok, Instagram Reels &amp; YouTube Shorts.<br>\n<img alt=\"✅\" src=\"https://web.telegram.org/a/img-apple-64/2705.png\"/> Being Confident On-Camera – Appear in videos, host engaging content, and connect with audiences.<br>\n<img alt=\"✅\" src=\"https://web.telegram.org/a/img-apple-64/2705.png\"/> Producing for Shoots – Assist in pre-production planning, coordinating logistics, and ensuring smooth execution.<br>\n<img alt=\"✅\" src=\"https://web.telegram.org/a/img-apple-64/2705.png\"/> Ad-Hoc Tasks – Contribute to various tasks that keep operations running efficiently.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Not a normal Internship.<br>\n<br>\n Performance Bonuses + Base – Get rewarded for content that drives views &amp; results.<br>\n Fast-Paced &amp; Dynamic – Ownership is everything in this high-speed start-up environment.<br>\n Young &amp; Adaptable – Always focusing on forward-looking strategies</p>",
